[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/stayman_transfers"]
[Student "S"]
{EAST has an invitational (9 point) hand with five \Ss.

She bids it in the standard way - first transfer WEST to \Ss, then invite 
the game by bidding 2NT.

WEST, with 17 points and three \Ss, accepts the game invitation and chooses 4\S.}

